                    <span>I saw Michael Webb on[tv]and had to buy this book right away. All the bookstores were sold out and I was grateful that Amazon[.com] still had some in stock.<P>I was charmed by Michael Webbs ideas on [that show] but even more so reading his book. It is obvious that he doesnt just make up ideas to fill pages of the book, but he comes up with these awesome ways of showing love for his wife because he really cares. <P>The book not only gave me great ideas, it make me more dedicated in my relationship so I could be more like Michael and his wife.</span>
                  
              
